879
00:34:47,520 --> 00:34:48,780
kind-hearted people.

880
00:34:49,080 --> 00:34:50,920
They often do generous deeds,

881
00:34:51,320 --> 00:34:54,159
and love to be a timely rain eager to help the needy.

882
00:34:54,520 --> 00:34:55,480
Just

883
00:34:55,840 --> 00:34:57,680
like a great benefactor.

884
00:34:57,880 --> 00:34:59,880
And I think at this critical moment,

885
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:00,800
Mr. Tian

886
00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:02,860
just happens to love the Baozi I make.

887
00:35:03,520 --> 00:35:05,160
This is Master's destiny.

888
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:08,280
Wanfu.

889
00:35:09,600 --> 00:35:11,080
I think you are the real

890
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:13,810
Timely Rain, Song Jiang, eager to help the needy.

891
00:35:15,800 --> 00:35:17,120
That dark and chubby guy?

892
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:17,880
I...

893
00:35:18,080 --> 00:35:19,540
I'm only about his height.

894
00:35:23,920 --> 00:35:24,560
By the way,

895
00:35:25,200 --> 00:35:26,460
you went to see Master?

896
00:35:27,000 --> 00:35:28,080
How is Master?

897
00:35:28,640 --> 00:35:29,960
Lawyer Wu said

898
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:32,760
he will write the apology letter for Master.

899
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:36,000
The hardest part now is

900
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:37,480
to get Master

901
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:39,480
to read it in person to the Japanese.

902
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:42,280
I don't know how to persuade him.

903
00:35:42,600 --> 00:35:44,680
I hope Lawyer Wu can.

904
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:46,920
If Master could be persuaded,

905
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:48,400
my surname wouldn't be Meng,

906
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:49,660
his wouldn't be Zhang,

907
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:51,370
and yours wouldn't be Ding.

908
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:54,560
I spent a whole night writing that letter.

909
00:35:54,880 --> 00:35:55,960
Every word

910
00:35:56,400 --> 00:35:57,720
cut me to the heart.

911
00:35:58,080 --> 00:35:59,340
Not to mention Master,

912
00:35:59,800 --> 00:36:01,960
even having me in front of the Japanese

913
00:36:01,960 --> 00:36:03,840
read that letter again

914
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:07,570
would be worse than killing me.

915
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,100
Then what should we do?

916
00:36:15,680 --> 00:36:17,540
This is a matter of life and death.

917
00:36:17,640 --> 00:36:20,120
We have to bow our heads even if we don't want to.

918
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,520
If Master can't be saved,

919
00:36:21,640 --> 00:36:22,720
isn't it all over?

920
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,440
Exactly.

921
00:36:24,880 --> 00:36:26,080
Living

922
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:29,200
is much harder than dying.

923
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:36,160
But

924
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:37,440
you're right.

925
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:40,440
If there's no sky,

926
00:36:41,080 --> 00:36:43,360
we'll scrape one out.

927
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:45,360
No matter what,

928
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,760
we still have to try.

929
00:36:47,480 --> 00:36:48,320
We can't just let Master

930
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,880
die in prison for nothing,

931
00:36:49,880 --> 00:36:50,480
right?

932
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:55,800
How could there be no sky?

933
00:36:56,560 --> 00:36:58,020
Isn't there still a crack?

934
00:36:58,120 --> 00:36:59,000
Pry it open.

935
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:00,120
Okay.

936
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:13,600
Maybe it lacks a bit of juice.

937
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:14,880
It's a bit dry.

938
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:27,740
I'll wrap some pork jelly inside.

939
00:37:27,880 --> 00:37:30,080
Once steamed, it'll be juicy, won't it?

940
00:38:04,840 --> 00:38:05,360
Brother,

941
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:07,240
I'm here to deliver Baozi to Mr. Tian.

942
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:08,880
I've already agreed with Mr. Tian.

943
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:09,740
You can't go in.

944
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:10,480
How about this?

945
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:12,080
You go in and report to Mr. Tian.

946
00:38:12,080 --> 00:38:13,080
He'll definitely let me in.

947
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:14,520
Just say a word, and it'll be fine.

948
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:16,250
No means no. Hurry up and leave.

949
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:17,160
This...

950
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:21,920
Brother Qi! Brother Qi!

951
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:23,880
I know Brother Qi.

952
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:24,720
Brother Qi! Brother Qi!

953
00:38:24,720 --> 00:38:25,200
What are you doing?

954
00:38:25,200 --> 00:38:25,880
Brother Qi! Brother Qi!

955
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:26,210
Stop!

956
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:26,600
Stop!

957
00:38:26,600 --> 00:38:27,260
Brother Qi!

958
00:38:27,600 --> 00:38:28,320
Brother Qi!

959
00:38:29,520 --> 00:38:30,200
Brother Qi!

960
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:32,200
Brother Qi!

961
00:38:32,600 --> 00:38:33,260
Brother Qi!

962
00:38:35,560 --> 00:38:36,240
Chef Meng.

963
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,080
Just call me Wanfu.

964
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:40,260
I'm here to deliver Baozi to Mr. Tian.

965
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:42,440
We agreed upstairs last time,

966
00:38:42,680 --> 00:38:44,320
to make him Seven Delicacies of Lanling,

967
00:38:44,320 --> 00:38:45,400
and deliver Baozi for seven days.

968
00:38:45,400 --> 00:38:46,660
Today is the first day.

969
00:38:46,720 --> 00:38:48,250
Okay, thank you, Chef Meng.

970
00:38:48,480 --> 00:38:49,140
Brother Qi,

971
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:51,880
can I say a word to Mr. Tian?

972
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:53,740
That day upstairs,

973
00:38:54,280 --> 00:38:55,080
There are too many people.

974
00:38:55,080 --> 00:38:56,680
I was too embarrassed to ask.

975
00:38:56,960 --> 00:38:59,040
Are you in some kind of trouble, Wanfu?

976
00:38:59,040 --> 00:39:00,880
Yes, huge trouble.

977
00:39:01,120 --> 00:39:01,720
I...

978
00:39:02,840 --> 00:39:05,040
I want to ask Mr. Tian to help me save someone.

979
00:39:05,040 --> 00:39:05,720
Who?

980
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:07,720
My father.

981
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:09,000
My father was mistaken by the Japanese

982
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:10,730
for an anti-Japanese element.

983
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:13,300
Now he is locked up in Pétain Police Station.

984
00:39:13,320 --> 00:39:15,600
Mr. Tian has no time for your trivial matters.

985
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:18,000
And don't mention the Seven Delicacies of Lanling again.

986
00:39:18,000 --> 00:39:18,680
Qi, Qi!

987
00:39:19,040 --> 00:39:20,170
Trouble is trouble,

988
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:21,040
baozi is baozi.

989
00:39:21,040 --> 00:39:22,440
I promised Mr. Tian I would make baozi for seven days.

990
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:23,600
I will do it for seven days.

991
00:39:23,600 --> 00:39:25,160
It's fine even if he doesn't help me.

992
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:27,040
Meng Wanfu, don't be ungrateful.

993
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:28,120
Go!

994
00:39:28,200 --> 00:39:28,680
No,

995
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:29,560
Qi.

996
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,090
Qi, please just help me.

997
00:39:31,160 --> 00:39:32,400
Please put in a good word with Mr. Tian for me.

998
00:39:32,400 --> 00:39:33,200
Qi!

999
00:39:36,760 --> 00:39:37,400
You...

1000
00:39:38,640 --> 00:39:39,570
You are Mr. Tian!

1001
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:41,840
Is your camera fixed?

1002
00:39:58,760 --> 00:39:59,440
Mr. Tian,

1003
00:39:59,720 --> 00:40:01,200
It's fine whether you help me or not.

1004
00:40:01,200 --> 00:40:02,160
Take the baozi.

1005
00:40:03,640 --> 00:40:04,400
If you don't think it tastes good,

1006
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,600
you can throw it away.

1007
00:40:05,640 --> 00:40:06,400
Thank you.

1008
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:15,120
Let's go.

1009
00:40:58,760 --> 00:40:59,760
Excuse me,

1010
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:01,440
I want to ask you...

1011
00:41:04,240 --> 00:41:05,040
Sister!

1012
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:05,960
Yujiao!

1013
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,160
Sister, why are you here?

1014
00:41:07,160 --> 00:41:07,920
Slow down.

1015
00:41:08,040 --> 00:41:09,560
Why are you doing this in the heavy rain?

1016
00:41:09,560 --> 00:41:10,840
Let's go inside.

1017
00:41:11,200 --> 00:41:12,200
No, I'm not going in.

1018
00:41:12,200 --> 00:41:13,930
I came to find you to tell you...

1019
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:14,800
It's okay.

1020
00:41:15,560 --> 00:41:17,760
Brigade Commander Zhang you asked me to find last time...

1021
00:41:17,760 --> 00:41:19,600
Didn't I mention Dr. Chen to you?

1022
00:41:20,040 --> 00:41:22,320
He recently returned to Shanghai from the countryside.

1023
00:41:22,320 --> 00:41:24,320
Let's go to the clinic to see him now.

1024
00:41:24,440 --> 00:41:25,840
Is it convenient for you?

1025
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:29,080
Wait for me a moment.

1026
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:31,080
Auntie Jing! Auntie Jing!

1027
00:41:31,160 --> 00:41:31,920
What's wrong?

1028
00:41:31,920 --> 00:41:33,120
Can you do me a favor?

1029
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,810
Help me look after Yueming.

1030
00:41:34,840 --> 00:41:35,840
Are you going out?

1031
00:41:36,640 --> 00:41:37,920
Then hurry up and go.

1032
00:41:38,440 --> 00:41:38,800
Okay.

1033
00:41:38,800 --> 00:41:39,930
Sister, wait for me.

1034
00:41:42,680 --> 00:41:43,440
Come here.

1035
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:46,760
Little girl, wait until the rain stops.

1036
00:42:05,160 --> 00:42:06,240
Madam Zhang, come.

1037
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:06,960
Thank you.

1038
00:42:07,520 --> 00:42:07,980
Xuefei.

1039
00:42:08,080 --> 00:42:08,760
Thank you.

1040
00:42:17,320 --> 00:42:19,280
When Xuefei first came to find me,

1041
00:42:20,400 --> 00:42:21,680
I completely refused.

1042
00:42:22,240 --> 00:42:25,240
Because the time I spent helping at the field hospital

1043
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:27,800
is the memory I want to escape from the most.

1044
00:42:28,440 --> 00:42:29,700
The Battle of Shanghai

1045
00:42:30,080 --> 00:42:31,760
was fought so fiercely,

1046
00:42:32,040 --> 00:42:33,640
beyond human imagination.

1047
00:42:34,520 --> 00:42:35,650
On the battlefield,

1048
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:38,000
soldiers used their flesh and blood

1049
00:42:38,080 --> 00:42:39,920
to fight the enemy's guns.

1050
00:42:40,440 --> 00:42:41,500
But I didn't expect

1051
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:43,810
that in our field hospital,

1052
00:42:44,240 --> 00:42:47,920
it was even bloodier and crueler than the frontlines.

1053
00:43:00,400 --> 00:43:02,760
This photo is too blurry.

1054
00:43:03,160 --> 00:43:04,240
I'm not sure.
